{"tid":1225831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建制派]韓國瑜：對香港政府能推遲就修訂逃犯條例立法表示肯定","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T12:47:16.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":231,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc7c7f4dc8a319d5167a7d04650871b6df31d10","tid":1225831,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"台灣高雄市長韓國瑜表示，對於香港政府能夠推遲就修訂逃犯條例立法，表示肯定，強調香港政府必須尊重香港民意，希望香港政府與香港人充分溝通，香港社會不要對立衝突。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜說，看著在街頭被暴力相向，但仍勇往直前的年輕孩子，必須力挺民主法治和人權。無論香港問題或台海關係，一旦脫離和平的可能，民主法治就失去希望。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜又說，台灣政黨與政客更不要刻意自我矮化，把一國兩制與台灣及香港相類比，不要一再抹紅在野黨，刻意製造台灣內部的衝突與對立。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463035-20190615.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463035-20190615.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=f0b59db4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463035-20190615.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=35e7718d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463035-20190615.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母真係建制派黎"},{"pid":"cd1b705e52d81131e25ebb47c8ec47f8e74029f6","tid":1225831,"uid":54344,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"你條奶共狗賣台灣就企過啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"172b115150b3dcd1cf741c52d1d41d803099659c","tid":1225831,"uid":103230,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"第一個衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4964583b1adc4b3e020390a468e2729d159d0308","tid":1225831,"uid":237562,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母做咩干涉別國內政"},{"pi